input_text.Prompt:
The following is a product description written by our marketing expert using the following product keywords and product title.

Product title:
ReadyPlug USB Cable Compatible with HP 1320 LaserJet Printer (10 Feet, Black)

Product keywords:
ReadyPlug Data Cable Compatible with HP 1320 LaserJet Printer
USB 2.0 High Speed Cable upto 480mbps
Length: 10 Feet (3 Meters) - Color: Black
Reduces strain on device port
Keeps cable out of the way
Protected from EMI/RFI interference
Uses an outer foil shield, inner braid shield and twisted-pair composition to ensure performance
For PC or Mac Computer

Product description:
input_text.Response A: This extra long ReadyPlug cable is guaranteed to work with the HP 1320 LaserJet Printer. This black USB 2.0 High Speed Cable (upto 480mbps) is 10 ft, allowing a connection a long way from your PC or Mac. The long length gives plenty of range for your connection, helps to reduce strain on the device port, and keeps the cable out of the way. Providing USB syncing to your HP 1320 LaserJet Printer, simply plug into any USB port and get connected. The cable is protected from EMI/RFI interference with an outer foil shield, inner braid shield and twisted-pair composition to ensure performance.
input_text.Response B: Are you tired of constantly having to check your HP 1320 LaserJet printer for new print jobs? With this 10-foot USB cable, you can reduce the strain on your device port and keep the cable out of the way. This cable is designed for high-speed data transfer, up to 480 Mbps, and is compatible with PC or Mac computers. It is also protected from EMI/RFI interference, using an outer foil shield, inner braid shield, and twisted-pair composition.
